# The canonical build runs from the REPO ROOT with explicit COPYs (see
# Dockerfile header), which is what actually bounds the image contents. This
# file exists per the service-directory convention and covers BuildKit's
# per-Dockerfile ignore lookup; patterns mirror what must never enter an image.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
tests/
.env
.env.*
